{"tid":1278332,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚前線online玩哨兵角色整親腰個位巴打","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T15:53:55.000Z","uid":110347,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0e1bebb7eacb21818c8a5ffbbf1994618d0795","tid":1278332,"uid":110347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係好想當面同你講聲對唔住！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為就係我攻城門推條鐵通個陣on9令到支鐵通挨左落你條腰到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個刻已經即刻同幾位同盟護送你去急救，一直同你講對唔住，但我諗你個刻應該痛到聽唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我一直係你附近睇住你，想等你狀態好啲再同你道歉同賠償，急救姐姐見我成日望住你就問我咩一會事，佢地了解左之後就叫我坐係社工個邊等你狀態再好啲先搵你，但過左陣就見唔番你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">巴打，我真係唔想你有事，我真係好想當面同你講句對唔住！你有咩事嘅所有醫藥費我會負責！就算你唔原諒我都好，求下你pm我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"8be26c136a634b68db190e7a8d0235f5405f0d56","tid":1278332,"uid":110347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de40fc121f6c58e27ff0e38cd856ab97281ab19a","tid":1278332,"uid":207077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:17:17.000Z","msg":"幫你推到搵到個巴打為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbba1d3cdeb57ff8e19653f2af921dcf3f60b9b2","tid":1278332,"uid":110347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de40fc121f6c58e27ff0e38cd856ab97281ab19a","tid":1278332,"uid":207077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:17:17.000Z","msg":"幫你推到搵到個巴打為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:26:33.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<im